data.description:
Welcome to this charming 1939 Avondale/Country Club home with timeless appeal!

This 2-story home boasts 3 beds, 1.5 baths, and 1,535 square feet of living space, with plenty of room for your family to live, grow, and make lasting memories.

The living room's gas-log fireplace is a cozy space to snuggle on cold Amarillo winter nights.  The adjacent dining and kitchen areas are set up for entertaining, with a large patio to extend the party to on warm summer nights. A 3-car detached garage has covered access to the back entry of the home.

Upstairs is a Master retreat, with landing, bedroom, walk-in closet, and half bath.  BONUS: laundry is UPSTAIRS! No running downstairs for clothes in the morning rush!

You could OWN this piece of HISTORY!

Schedule showing TODAY!
